  <title>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Build a children&apos;s army to fight global warming</narrative>
  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">Trees can have a huge impact on climate change, both locally and globally. By helping students at schools in southern India plant and nurture trees, we will not only enlist the power of trees to mitigate climate change but educate the next generation about the importance of increasing green cover. The trees they plant will have an immediate impact, while the seeds we plant in their young minds will bear fruit long into the future.</narrative>
  </description>
